# Template — Variables de entorno por cliente

Copiar a `.env` en el servidor de la instancia. Ajustar valores marcados con `<...>`.

```env
APP_NAME="<CLIENT_DISPLAY_NAME> Middleware"
APP_ENV=production
APP_KEY=<php artisan key:generate --show>
APP_DEBUG=false
APP_URL=https://<client-slug>.middleware.example.com
APP_TIMEZONE=America/Lima

LOG_CHANNEL=stack
LOG_LEVEL=info

PLATFORM_CLIENT_SLUG=<client-slug>
PLATFORM_CLIENT_NAME="<CLIENT_DISPLAY_NAME>"
PLATFORM_DEPLOYMENT_MODE=instance_per_client
PLATFORM_SEED_INSTANCE_TENANT=true

DB_CONNECTION=mysql
DB_HOST=<db-host>
DB_PORT=3306
DB_DATABASE=platform_<client-slug>
DB_USERNAME=<db-user>
DB_PASSWORD=<db-password>

QUEUE_CONNECTION=redis
REDIS_HOST=<redis-host>
REDIS_PASSWORD=<redis-password>
REDIS_PORT=6379

CACHE_STORE=redis
SESSION_DRIVER=redis
```

Tras copiar:

```bash
php artisan key:generate
php artisan migrate --force
php artisan db:seed --force
php artisan platform:ensure-instance-tenant
php artisan config:cache
```

Ver [Runbook_Onboarding_Cliente.md](../Runbook_Onboarding_Cliente.md).
